snippet.title: Rune Fencer Illyia - Official Trailer | Future of Play Direct 2023
snippet.description:
See combat, capybaras, fishing, and much more in this trailer for Rune Fencer Illyia, an upcoming Metroidvania game. In Rune Fencer Illyia, steal enemy abilities and fight them back with their own runic magic and deadly swordplay. Rune Fencer Illyia is coming to PC, PlayStation, Nintendo Switch, and Xbox.

#GameTrailers #SoG #Gaming
